Recently, GPT-4's capabilities for KBC and reasoning were examined [autokg2023]. This research compared GPT-3, ChatGPT, and GPT-4 on information extraction tasks, KBC, and KG-based question answering.
However, these studies focus on popular statements from existing KBs, neglecting the challenge of introducing genuinely new knowledge in the long tail.